data.description: This is your chance to own your own wooded retreat near the beach with this .45 acre wooded lot in Carolina Shores. This ranch style home includes recent updates including landscaping, interior paint, flooring, and light fixtures. The living room and family rooms are a perfect gathering place separated by a 2-sided whitewashed fireplace, they boast a cathedral ceiling, transom windows for plenty of light and plantation shutters. The kitchen includes quartz counters, an island with a cook top, a newer stainless-steel hood, and a wall oven. There is plenty of cabinet space and a pantry. The master suite includes an en-suite bathroom with a large walk-in tiled shower and skylights for plenty of natural light. Enjoy the outdoors in the 3-season Carolina room, accessible from both the dining room and master bedroom. Both the front and back yards provide year-round privacy with trees, bushes, and flowering shrubs. Enjoy minimal grass cutting due to the updated landscaping. Carolina Shores is a golf community where homeowners enjoy an active lifestyle with a clubhouse, pool, tennis, pickleball and much more. Carolina Shores is located minutes from the shopping and restaurants of downtown Calabash, only 6 miles to Sunset Beach, and a short drive to the attractions of the Myrtle Beach area.
